author: Legolauncher
title: Awesome set
review:
This set really stands apart from any other duplo sets. It is so much fun to play with and think of ways to build with these unique pieces.

My toddler lovvvvves it, but is a bit young to figure out how to use the screwdrivers. As an adult, it makes playtime a lot more fun and interesting.

I found it on sale online for ~$80 at Discount School Supplies. Amazing price for a set this big and the tech that goes into it.
